        <item>
            <title>1.4</title>
            <pubDate>Thu, 04 Jun 2026 06:17:53 -0700</pubDate>
            <sparkle:version>5</sparkle:version>
            <sparkle:shortVersionString>1.4</sparkle:shortVersionString>
            <sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>13.0</sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>
            <description sparkle:format="markdown"><![CDATA[## Uptick 1.4

**Fixes a new-day glitch**
- After your Mac slept overnight, Uptick could keep showing **yesterday's** total — and the Pacing tab would project a wildly inflated end-of-day number. Fixed: Uptick now refreshes the moment your Mac wakes, rolls over cleanly at the start of each day (Pacific), and never displays a figure that isn't actually today's.

**Universal app**
- Uptick is now a **universal binary** — it runs natively on both **Apple Silicon** and **Intel** Macs. Still requires macOS 13 (Ventura) or later.
]]></description>
