        <item>
            <title>1.2</title>
            <pubDate>Tue, 02 Jun 2026 16:55:04 -0400</pubDate>
            <sparkle:version>3</sparkle:version>
            <sparkle:shortVersionString>1.2</sparkle:shortVersionString>
            <sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>13.0</sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>
            <sparkle:hardwareRequirements>arm64</sparkle:hardwareRequirements>
            <description sparkle:format="markdown"><![CDATA[## Uptick 1.2

**Pacing, reimagined**
- Compare today against **Yesterday**, a rolling **N-day average** (grows from your history up to 7 days), **All-time average**, and **any specific day** via the new dropdown — each a toggleable line.
- New **"ahead / behind"** badges for both yesterday and the rolling average.
- **Momentum arrows** in the tooltip show, hour by hour, whether you're gaining ground or slipping behind each line.
- Hover anywhere on the chart: the tooltip **snaps to clean hourly points**, reads every visible line at that time, and shows the gap to today.
- All series are aligned to a consistent **hourly grid** for a cleaner, comparable story.
- Times are shown in **Pacific** to match Amazon's reporting day.
]]></description>
