            <description sparkle:format="markdown"><![CDATA[## Uptick 1.1

**Pacing got smarter**
- Times now match Amazon (Pacific time) so the day-over-day comparison lines up.
- The "vs yesterday" badge compares today against yesterday *at the same time of day*.
- Smarter end-of-day projection based on yesterday's shape.
- Fixed the hover tooltip — it now tracks your cursor and shows the right values.

**Overview table**
- Switching Group By and changing pages is instant now (cached), with a clean loading state.
- Added a refresh button.

**Sign in**
- Paste (⌘V) now works in the sign-in window.
- "Sign in again" fully signs out and back in; clearer signed-in confirmation.

**Under the hood**
- Automatic updates (you're using them right now 🎉).
]]></description>
